SCORE Down for December 2001 <http://www.rigzone.com/news/article.asp?a_id=2439>
Houston-based international offshore drilling contractor GlobalSantaFe reported that the company's worldwide SCORE for December 2001 was down from the previous month's SCORE by 1.7 percent. 

