Westcoast Energy Reaches Milestone in Mexico <http://www.rigzone.com/news/article.asp?a_id=2447>
Westcoast Energy announced has reached a major milestone in the ! development of the Campeche Natural Gas Compression Services Project in Mexico.

Statfjord C Shutdown  <http://www.rigzone.com/news/article.asp?a_id=2443>
Production from Statfjord C has been shut down after find corrosion damage in the flare system.

Dragon Oil Carries Out Production Testing in Caspian Sea <http://www.rigzone.com/news/article.asp?a_id=2440>
Dragon Oil has begun a 10-day testing program of its LAM 22-102 well in the Caspian Sea.

