Thomas O'Malley Resigns From Phillips <http://www.rigzone.com/news/article.asp?a_id=2442>
Thomas O'Malley has resigned from the Phillips Board of Directors to pursue other avenues in the energy industry.

Oil Search and Orogen Minerals Agree to Merge <http://www.rigzone.com/news/article.asp?a_id=2441>Oil Search and Orogen Minerals have agreed to merge in a deal valued at A1.4 billion.

